plexity theory to\nthe domain of answer set programming.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Apr 2011 14:59:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 29 Mar 2012 19:55:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 May 2012 17:23:05 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 6 Mar 2014 17:39:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-07"}
